snippet.title: No Strangers Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Store Page:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3127650/NO_STRANGERS/

Hello friends.

I wanted to share with you the latest trailer video of my multiplayer who's the killer themed FPS RPG No Strangers. 

The game will be released in September. To support, I would appreciate it if you visit the store page and add it to your wishlist.
